      <data key="d1">"Scarface is a gray langur monkey characterized by its distinctive facial markings, significant in its social dynamics and engagements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scarface is an individual baboon characterized by distinctive facial markings, known for his victories within the social hierarchy among baboons."</data>
