      <data key="d1">"Playful Interaction denotes the behaviors zebras display when engaging socially, whether in a friendly manner or as part of their social hierarchy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Playful Interaction depicts the engaging behavior of langurs as they interact socially within their group, showcasing their playful demeanor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Playful Interactions among young kangaroos involve activities that promote agility and social bonding, important for their development."</data>
