    <node id="&quot;NATURAL BEHAVIOR&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Natural Behavior encompasses the instinctive actions exhibited by langurs, baboons, and guanacos in their habitats, relating to survival, socializing, and reproduction."&lt;SEP&gt;"Natural Behavior encompasses the instinctual actions and reactions of guanacos in their environment, including grazing, running, and social interactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Natural Behavior encompasses the instinctual activities of animals interacting in their ecosystems, including hunting and foraging."</data>
