      <data key="d1">"Agility is a crucial attribute for animals like the Ibex and Cheetah, allowing them to navigate challenging terrains and successfully evade or catch prey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Agility refers to the ability of the guanaco to move quickly and easily, which is demonstrated in their rapid movements and adaptations to their environment."</data>
