    </node>
    <node id="&quot;POSSUM&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ANIMAL"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Possum is depicted as a small marsupial residing in a tree trunk, indicated by its alert demeanor and protective behavior towards its young."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Possum is portrayed as a prey animal, startled yet resilient while being confronted by the Water Lizard in its nest."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e5ec702f1741aa9901cb587276f06451&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0fa7e68b98ad851a5f1ad7067bdfb774</data>
